flowchart TD
    A[User Prompt] --> B{Existing classification?}

    B -->|No| C[IntentClassifier.classify]
    B -->|Yes, locked| Z[Skip: reuse locked classification]

    C --> D[ProjectScanner.scan]
    C --> E[TechDetector.detect]

    D --> F[Multi-Axis Type Scoring]
    E --> F

    F --> G["Score: web-ui (0.85)"]
    F --> H["Score: canvas-game (0.30)"]
    F --> I["Score: backend-api (0.10)"]

    G & H & I --> J[Sort by descending score]

    J --> K{"Confidence check"}
    K -->|"score > 0.8 AND no alternatives"| L["confidence: high<br/>no alternatives shown"]
    K -->|"score > 0.5"| M["confidence: medium<br/>1-2 alternatives shown"]
    K -->|"score < 0.5"| N["confidence: low<br/>interactive selection"]

    L & M & N --> O[DensityAnalyzer.analyze]
    O --> P[Subsystem estimate]

    P --> Q[WorkflowRegistry.route]
    Q --> R[Build classification object]

    R --> S[HITL Renderer]
    S --> T{"User response"}

    T -->|"confirm: ok/yes/确认"| U["Lock classification<br/>fsm → discovery"]
    T -->|"adjust: type:game"| V["Re-classify with adjustments<br/>fsm: back to classifying"]
    T -->|"select: A/B/C"| W["Apply selection<br/>fsm → discovery"]
    T -->|"reclassify: restart"| C
    T -->|"unknown response"| S

    U --> X[Task proceeds with locked classification]
    X --> Y[Done]
